{"tid":1361620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【727元朗見】起初，白衫打元朗人的時候，我躲在屋企，因為我不是元朗人。","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T23:47:37.000Z","uid":271829,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0de8be18e1fbeafee8195922775ba5fd1b1226ca","tid":1361620,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"起初，白衫打元朗人的時候，<br />\n我躲在家裏，因為我不是元朗人。<br />\n<br />\n當他們打離島人的時候，<br />\n我躲在家裏，因為我不是離島人。<br />\n<br />\n當他們打九龍人的時候，<br />\n我躲在家裏，因為我不是九龍人。<br />\n<br />\n當他們打香港島人的時候，<br />\n我躲在家裏，因為我不是香港島人。<br />\n<br />\n最後當他們來我家時，<br />\n再也沒有人能站起來保護我了。"},{"pid":"25c2f913c5416ba06cf7d1dcf30b05ea8f3289f0","tid":1361620,"uid":276264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:09.000Z","msg":"得啦，27號見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99556f3737d95e2a1f7e7a34db1bdd0b4050e6b5","tid":1361620,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:09:16.000Z","msg":"從來淨係聽過有軍政府，<br />\n香港就發明咗警政府同黑政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9b11449581e21fd20341f38c8bdf0ba346011a","tid":1361620,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:57:28.000Z","msg":"冇不反對通知書都要入去食燒鵝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66175f607662b1c78a96f4a88770c2c0e8fe8f80","tid":1361620,"uid":263485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"最後當他們來我家時，我和他們一起出去打人了。"},{"pid":"980b5a5f0b4dbe2998ba5041da498eb35d64259a","tid":1361620,"uid":236780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba9b11449581e21fd20341f38c8bdf0ba346011a","tid":1361620,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:57:28.000Z","msg":"冇不反對通知書都要入去食燒鵝 <img